{
  "text": "The transplantation of cryo-preserved ovarian tissue is an outpatient procedure that restores hormonal function and fertility [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . After ovarian tissue transplantation women are able to conceive normally without medical assistance [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . The oocyte and ovarian tissue cryopreservation may expand the reproductive life-span for women who wish to delay childbearing.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "20293806",
